00409.jpg\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"proof__inner\">\n<p class=\"proof__desc\">\n                  세라마이드 워터가 수분을 공급하고 라벤더 오일이 수분이 날아가는 것을 보호하여 눈가 피부를 유연하고 촉촉하게 만들어 줍니다.\n                </p>\n<div class=\"proof__cont\">\n<em class=\"proof__cap\">SECRET 3.</em>\n<span class=\"proof__t\">연약한 눈가를 촉촉하고 매끄럽게 보호하는 세라마이드 워터</span>\n<button class=\"proof__btn\" type=\"button\">\n<span class=\"more\"></span>\n<span class=\"a11y\">더보기</span>\n</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"ft-data ft-data--speech\" style=\"color: #4477be;\">\n<div class=\"bg\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background-color: #e6ecf8;\">\n<div class=\"bg__moving\" style=\"color: rgb(203, 212, 229); width: 2292.48px;\">\n<div class=\"bg__marquee-wrap\" style=\"transform: translate3d(-48.9853px, 0px, 0px);\">\n<span class=\"bg__marquee\">\n<span class=\"bg__tag\">#어린눈가솔루션</span>\n<span class=\"bg__tag\">#동안아이세럼</span>\n<span class=\"bg__tag\">#잔주름케어세럼</span>\n<span class=\"bg__tag\">#어린눈가솔루션</span><span class=\"bg__tag\">#동안아이세럼</span><span class=\"bg__tag\">#잔주름케어세럼</span></span>\n<span class=\"bg__marquee\">\n<span class=\"bg__tag\">#어린눈가솔루션</span>\n<span class=\"bg__tag\">#동안아이세럼</span>\n<span class=\"bg__tag\">#잔주름케어세럼</span>\n<span class=\"bg__tag\">#어린눈가솔루션</span><span class=\"bg__tag\">#동안아이세럼</span><span class=\"bg__tag\">#잔주름케어세럼</span></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ft-data__pad\">\n<header class=\"pdp__sub-header\">\n<em class=\"pdp__sub-cap\">Clinical Data</em>\n<h3 class=\"h4 pdp__sub-heading\">퍼펙트 리뉴 아이세럼 EX 고객 사용 만족도</h3>\n</header>\n<div class=\"ft-data__cont\">\n<img alt=\"퍼펙트 리뉴 아이세럼 EX\" class=\"ft-data__center\" src=\"/kr/ko/assets/pdp/skincare/201911/perfect-renew-eye-serum-clinical.png\"/>\n<div class=\"speech\">\n<span class=\"speech__text\">\n<span class=\"u-br\">이제품의 결+보습 효과에 만족한다.</span>\n<span class=\"u-br\"><em>95.4%</em></span>\n</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"speech\">\n<span class=\"speech__text\">\n<span class=\"u-br\">이 제품을 지인에게 소개해주고 