btn\" type=\"button\">\n<span class=\"more\"></span>\n<span class=\"a11y\">더보기</span>\n</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"proof\">\n<div class=\"proof__bg\">\n<img alt=\"부드럽게 발리며, 윤기나는 피부\" src=\"/kr/ko/skincare/__icsFiles/afieldfile/2019/11/17/Time_Freeze_Skin_Refiner_rtb_03.png\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"proof__inner\">\n<p class=\"proof__desc\">\n                  피부에 부드럽게 발리는 제형으로 피부에 힘을 길러 건강하고 윤기나는 탱탱한 피부로 가꾸어줍니다.\n                </p>\n<div class=\"proof__cont\">\n<em class=\"proof__cap\">SECRET 3.</em>\n<span class=\"proof__t\">부드럽게 발리며, 윤기나는 피부</span>\n<button class=\"proof__btn\" type=\"button\">\n<span class=\"more\"></span>\n<span class=\"a11y\">더보기</span>\n</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"ft-texture\">\n<div class=\"wrapper wrapper--10-over-12\">\n<header class=\"pdp__sub-header\">\n<em class=\"pdp__sub-cap\">TEXTURE</em>\n<h3 class=\"h4 pdp__sub-heading\">불투명한 젤 타입의 고점도 스킨</h3>\n</header>\n<div class=\"texture__gallery\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"texture__item col-md-3-6\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/kr/ko/assets/pdp/skincare/201911/time-freeze-skin-refiner-texture-01.gif\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"texture__item col-md-3-6\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/kr/ko/assets/pdp/skincare/201911/time-freeze-skin-refiner-texture-02.gif\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ft-step\">\n<div class=\"bg\" role=\"presentation\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"bg__img\" src=\"/kr/ko/assets/pdp/beststep-bg.jpg\"/>\n</div>\n<header class=\"pdp__sub-header\">\n<em class=\"pdp__sub-cap\">BEST STEP</em>\n<h3 class=\"h4 pdp__sub-header\">\n            라네즈가 추천하는 탄력 업 스텝\n          </h3>\n</header>\n<div class=\"swiper-container ft-step__carousel swiper-container-initialized swiper-container-horizontal\" data-initial-step=\"0\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\" style=\"transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\">\n<a ap-click-area=\"Product\" ap-click-data=\"스텝_Time Freeze Skin